# CI/CD Pipeline Status
# Generated: 2026-05-28
# Version: 1.0.0

## Deliverables

### 1. GitHub Actions Workflows ✅
- `.github/workflows/ci.yml` — Full CI (lint, test, build, scan, infra validate)
- `.github/workflows/pr-checks.yml` — PR validation (fast lint, tests, dependency review, secrets)
- `.github/workflows/cd-staging.yml` — Auto deploy to staging on develop push
- `.github/workflows/cd-production.yml` — Manual deploy to production with approval gates

### 2. Deployment Scripts ✅
- `scripts/deploy-staging.sh` — CLI deploy to staging
- `scripts/deploy-production.sh` — CLI deploy to production (canary/blue-green/rolling)
- `scripts/rollback.sh` — Rollback production deployment

### 3. Environment Configs ✅
- `infra/k8s/base/kustomization.yaml` — Shared base
- `infra/k8s/staging/` — Staging overlay (replicas, resources, ingress, env)
- `infra/k8s/production/` — Production overlay (strict network policies, PDB, resources)

### 4. Monitoring Integration ✅
- `infra/k8s/monitoring/servicemonitor.yaml` — Prometheus scraping config
- `infra/k8s/monitoring/prometheusrules.yaml` — Alert rules (critical/high/medium)
- `infra/k8s/monitoring/probes.yaml` — Liveness/readiness/startup probes
- `infra/k8s/monitoring/health-checks.yaml` — Health check config + network policy

### 5. Documentation ✅
- `docs/devops/ci-cd.md` — CI/CD pipeline documentation
- `docs/devops/deployment.md` — Deployment guide

## Status: COMPLETE
